    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/4dbf21bbd8444b1b6821ba6358d532c5.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/4dbf21bbd8444b1b6821ba6358d532c5.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span>首先，我们由衷地希望您会拥有温馨而愉快的购物体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，在您做出决定之前，我们在此真诚提示......</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>如果您认为这是一款游戏，<u><i>请您千万不要购买它！</i></u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相反地，如果您接受它成为您......</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人生中的第一款<u><i>电子香水</i></u>，</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并在您需要感受一种梦核奇妙氛围的时候，打开它走上几步，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们会非常开心并乐意您选择它！</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：本电子香水套装包含由几十种环境音效，脚步声，上万级台阶构建而成的三瓶香水，它们分别是：<strong>MONTAGE, PleaseTravelersSafe&amp;sounD, CANDY</strong>，并附赠一瓶<strong>小样</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，让我们一起回到那个令人好奇的问题：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>请问，人们会经常梦到楼梯吗？</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/a5907d4bd8d2d8f997405d5e14761a25.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/a5907d4bd8d2d8f997405d5e14761a25.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/dbc4aced07b263b60e215272710e6e8c.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/dbc4aced07b263b60e215272710e6e8c.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/a146d67f340018332a0b0208148afb44.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/a146d67f340018332a0b0208148afb44.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/62f3da0919c40e9a5c328f72108fa08e.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/62f3da0919c40e9a5c328f72108fa08e.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
